$AU{C_G} = {\ }\sum i{\ } = {\ }1n - 1\left({{m_{(i +1)}} + {m_i}} \right) \cdot {t_i}2$\end{document}, where ti denotes the individual time distance between measurements, mi denotes the individual measurement, and n represents the total number of measures. In line with recommendations before calculating cortisol, concentrations exceeding 2.5 SD from the mean of each sample time (ST) were excluded from the dataset before calculating the AUCG and DCS.80–82
